        <title>LXC container directory related</title>
        <author>
            <name>Jack Chan</name>
        </author>
        <link href="https://ckc.github.io/lxc-container-directory-related/"/>
        <id>https://ckc.github.io/lxc-container-directory-related/</id>
            <category term="Container"/>

        <updated>2022-05-25T07:39:25+08:00</updated>
            <summary>
                <![CDATA[
                    Default: /var/cache/lxc Ref: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/25286546/change-lxc-container-directory 
                ]]>
            </summary>
        <content type="html">
            <![CDATA[
                <p>Default: /var/cache/lxc</p>
<ol>
<li><code>lxc.lxcpath</code> in <code>/etc/lxc/lxc.conf</code>, consult <code>man lxc.system.conf</code> for details.</li>
<li><code>lxc-*</code> tools accepts <code>-P</code> flag to specify alternate container path.</li>
<li><code>lxc-create</code> <code>-B dir</code> backing store has optional <code>--dir ROOTFS</code> flag.</li>
</ol>
<p> </p>
<p>Ref: <a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/25286546/change-lxc-container-directory">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/25286546/change-lxc-container-directory</a> </p>
