            <category term="MariaDB"/>

        <updated>2022-06-02T13:21:11+08:00</updated>
            <summary>
                <![CDATA[
                        <img src="https://ckc.github.io/media/posts/5/mariadb-galera-cluster-1024x545.png" alt="" />
                    1. Linux OS level pre-config sudo vim /etc/hosts 10.0.1.102 mariadb-node1.ckc.im mariadb-node1 10.0.1.103 mariadb-node2.ckc.im mariadb-node2 10.0.1.204 mariadb-node3.ckc.im mariadb-node3 config A record set correct target DNS for each node sudo apt update sudo apt -y install mariadb-server mariadb-client sudo mysql_secure_installation mariadb-node1 sudo vim /etc/mysql/mariadb.conf.d/50-server.cnf mariadb-node2 sudo vim&hellip;
                ]]>
            </summary>
        <content type="html">
            <![CDATA[
                    <img src="https://ckc.github.io/media/posts/5/mariadb-galera-cluster-1024x545.png" alt="" />
                <p><img loading="lazy" src="https://computingforgeeks.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/mariadb-galera-cluster-1024x545.png?ezimgfmt=rs:696x370/rscb23/ng:webp/ngcb23" data-is-external-image="true"  alt="mariadb galera cluster"></p>
